            "title": "盤中速報 - 嘉基(6715)大漲7.75%，報459元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>嘉基(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6715-TW</a>)20日09:40股價上漲33元，報459.0元，漲幅7.75%，成交851張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>嘉基(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6715-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為高速電/光傳輸線及連接器相關產品之研發、生產與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌2.96%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.91%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-338 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1,239 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+942 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-41 張</li> <li>融資增減：-141 張</li> <li>融券增減：-92 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
